  "text": "Regional tissue oxygen saturation (rSO 2 ) was continuously monitored by the in vivo optical spectroscopy (INVOS) system. [CITATION_1] The level of rSO 2 was maintained during SCP. As a result, the patient recovered smoothly without any new cerebral deficits.",
